        <updateDate>2019-08-15T15:43:43Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Comprehensive Listing of Evidence for Assessments of Regulations Act or the CLEAR Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires each federal agency to publish the research source code, data, and documents it used when assessing a new regulation, such as in an assessment of the costs and benefits of the regulation. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
